<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Climate Solutions</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
  </head>
  <body>

    <%- include('partials/navbar', {page: '/home'}) %>

  

    <div class="container mx-auto px-3 py-7">
                 
      <div class="hero bg-base-200 py-10 mb-12 rounded-lg">
        <div class="hero-content text-center">
          <div class="max-w-md">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Hello there</h1>
            <p class="py-6">
              Check out these wonderful projects aiming to help our environment!
            </p>
            <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary">
            See projects!
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

   
  <div class="grid gap-6 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
   
    <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
      <figure>
        <img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_farmlandrestoration01.jpg" alt="Project 1" />
      </figure>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Abandoned Farmland Restoration</h2>
        <p>Restoration can bring degraded farmland back into productivity and sequester carbon in the process.</p>
        <div class="card-actions justify-end">
          <a href="/solutions/projects/1" class="btn btn-outline btn-primary">More Info</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

   
    <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
      <figure>
        <img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/airplanes-web.jpg" alt="Project 13" />
      </figure>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Efficient Aviation</h2>
        <p>Technologies and practices that can lower airplane emissions include better engines, wingtips, and reducing airplanes’ weight.</p>
        <div class="card-actions justify-end">
          <a href="/solutions/projects/13" class="btn btn-outline btn-primary">More Info</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    
    <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
      <figure>
        <img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_perennialbiomass01.jpg" alt="Project 26" />
      </figure>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Perennial Biomass Production</h2>
        <p>Bioenergy relies on biomass—often annual crops such as corn. Perennial plants (e.g., switchgrass, silvergrass, willow, eucalyptus) are a more sustainable source and sequester modest amounts of soil carbon.</p>
        <div class="card-actions justify-end">
          <a href="/solutions/projects/26" class="btn btn-outline btn-primary"> More Info</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>
